OncoSimX Workset Class

Source: R/R6ClassModelTask.R, R/R6ClassWorkset.R
load_workset.Rd

OncoSimX Workset Class

Usage

load_workset(model, set)

load_scenario(model, set)

Arguments

model

Model digest or model name.

set

Name of workset (input set of model parameters).

Value

An OncoSimXWorkset instance.

Details

load_scenario() is an alias for load_workset().

Method run()

Run scenario

Usage

OncoSimXWorkset$run(
  name,
  opts = opts_run(),
  wait = FALSE,
  wait_time = 0.2,
  progress = TRUE
)

Arguments

name

Run name.

opts

Run options.

wait

Logical. Should we wait until the model run is done?

wait_time

Number of seconds to wait between status checks.

progress

Logical. Should a progress bar be shown?

Returns

Self, invisibly.
